# Note grammar

@IMPORT ./query_string.cpp.hcg as Query

<> goal → note

<> note → type? Query::container_clause? \; tags? \; data?			↦c ^NOTE_Note

<> type → Query::number

<> tags → tag 														↦r ^NOTE_TagList
	│ tags , tag													↦r ^NOTE_TagList

<> tag → Query::sentence \= Query::number 					↦r ^NOTE_TagNumber
	│ Query::sentence \= Query::sentence 					↦r ^NOTE_TagString
	│ Query::sentence 										↦r ^NOTE_Tag

<> data → Query::sentence									↦r ^NOTE_Body